      "tree_id": "f7631bf5d6191c3105acc9ef7eaea1ab07fb56c1",
      "distinct": true,
      "message": "docs(desktop): fix README env-file path inconsistency\n\nCodeRabbit blocker on PR #621: README said to create\napps/desktop/.env.development but the with-env script loads\napps/desktop/.vercel/.env.development.local. Contributors following the\ndocs would boot without NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY and hit the\nt3-env banner at startup.\n\nPoint README at .env.example + .vercel/.env.development.local to match\nthe with-env script. Also clarify that VITE_LIGHTFAST_API_URL is optional\n(defaulted by the renderer env schema) — the real required var is\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY for the main process.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-24T20:03:05+10:00",
      "url": "https://github.com/lightfastai/lightfast/commit/20c56310fb378b44432f66c909dd5273468bdc4f",
